间编辑要求每课示例代码可独立运行，不依赖外部服务\n- 每节课代码行数控制在 400 行以内，超出需拆模块\n</memory_index>\nYour personal goal is: 帮助晓寒高效完成各类任务，严谨、结果导向'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': '\nCurrent Task: 帮我调研极客时间平台上多智能体相关课程的现状，生成一份调研报告保存到文件\n\nThis is the expected criteria for your final answer: 针对用户请求的完整回复\nyou MUST return the actual complete content as the final answer, not a summary.'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'tool_calls': [{'id': 'call_dfdd2633453e4558bce131cc', 'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'search_web', 'arguments': '{"query": "极客时间 多智能体 课程", "top_k": "10", "recency_filter": "year", "sites": "[\\"time.geekbang.org\\"]"}'}}]}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_dfdd2633453e4558bce131cc', 'name': 'search_web', 'content': '[已剪枝]'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Analyze the tool result. If requirements are met, provide the Final Answer. Otherwise, call the next tool. Deliver only the answer without meta-commentary.'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'tool_calls': [{'id': 'call_c4f3f9bda42949e599b35c8b', 'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'search_web', 'arguments': '{"query": "极客时间 多智能体 课程", "top_k": "10", "recency_filter": "year", "sites": "None"}'}}]}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_c4f3f9bda42949e599b35c8b', 'name': 'search_web', 'content': '错误：API返回错误。\n原因：百度搜索API返回错误码InvalidArgument，错误信息：json: cannot unmarshal string into Go struct field SearchResource.resource_type_filter.top_k of type int，请求ID：19b852bd-d2fa-4690-86a1-db49800685b5。\n解决提示：请检查请求参数是否正确，或稍后重试\n'}, {'role': 'user', 'content': 'Analyze the tool result. If requirements are met, provide the Final Answer. Otherwise, call the next tool. Deliver only the answer without meta-commentary.'}, {'role': 'assistant', 'content': None, 'tool_calls': [{'id': 'call_0bc5108f1c5a47f89f2eb9e2', 'type': 'function', 'function': {'name': 'search_web', 'arguments': '{"query": "极客时间 多智能体 课程", "top_k": "10", "recency_filter": "None", "sites": "None"}'}}]}, {'role': 'tool', 'tool_call_id': 'call_0bc5108f1c5a47f89